ove, and in alphabetical order, L is the 12th letter and links the letters K (EXO-K) and M (EXO-M). EXO-L is considered a sub-unit of EXO, so that EXO-K + EXO-L + EXO-M = One. As in the band's slogan \"WE ARE ONE!\", meaning the band members and the fans are ONE.\n|<ref>{{cite web|url= http://www.allkpop.com/article/2014/08/exo-announce-fanclub-name-exo-l|title= [Updated] EXO announce fanclub name, 'EXO-L'?|website= Allkpop|author= serendipity|date= 5 August 2014}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[Fall Out Boy]]\n|Youngbloods\n|music band\n|\n|<ref name=\"billboard\" />\n|-\n|[[FC Barcelona]]\n|[[Supporters of FC Barcelona|Cul\u00e9s]]\n|sports team\n|\n|<ref>{{Cite AV media|title= Bar\u00e7a Dreams, a veritable history of FC Barcelona|author= Jordi Llompart|year= 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[Scuderia Ferrari]]\n|[[Tifosi]]\n|sports team\n|\n|<ref>{{cite web |url=http://en.espn.co.uk/italy/motorsport/story/174495.html |title=Tifosi deserved better from Ferrari - Alonso |author=<!--Staff writer(s); no by-line.--> |date=7 September 2014 |website=[[ESPN (UK TV channel)]] |access-date=2017-01-09}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[Feyenoord]]\n|[[Het Legioen]]\n|sports team\n|\n|<ref>{{cite web |url=http://metro.co.uk/2012/02/10/feyenoord-fans-sign-up-for-man-citys-john-guidetti-to-stay-315774/ |title=Feyenoord fans sign up for Man City\u2019s John Guidetti to stay |author=<!--Staff writer(s); no by-line.--> |date=10 February 2012 |website=[[metro.co.uk]]|access-date=2017-01-11}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[Fifth Harmony]]\n|Harmonizers\n|music band\n|\n|<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/events/fan-army/6634761/fifth-harmony-fans-harmonizers-worth-it|title=Fifth Harmony Gushes Over 'Smart, Passionate' Fan Base|newspaper=Billboard|access-date=2016-11-29}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[Final Space]]\n|Fantrexians\n|TV show\n|\n|<ref>{{cite web|url= https://twitter.com/KasterosePrsnl/status/994287270730481664|title= [Fantrexian Name Creator]|website= Twitter|author= Tenth Dutchor|date= 9 May 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n|''[[Firefly (TV s